      </div>
      <div class="guideline-card">
        <h4>Screen Readers</h4>
        <p>Include proper <code>aria-label</code> attributes to describe the persona to assistive technology.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="code-block">
      <pre><code>&lt;div
  class="avatar avatar--ferni"
  role="img"
  aria-label="Ferni, Chief of Staff"
&gt;
  &lt;span class="avatar-initial" aria-hidden="true"&gt;F&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>
